OL,3,CRescues of people from vehicles in
OL,4,Cfloods doubles since before pandemic `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FFire brigade rescues from vehicles
OL,8,Fcaught in floods in England have
OL,9,Fdoubled since before the coronavirus
OL,10,Fpandemic, according to new research.
OL,12,FAA analysis of Government figures
OL,13,Fshows there was an annual average of
OL,14,F323 incidents of firefighters saving
OL,15,Fpeople from cars in floodwater during
OL,16,Fthe three years to the end of March.
OL,18,FThat is compared with an average of
OL,19,F161 in the 10 years to the end of
OL,20,FMarch 2019.
