OL,3,CRescues of people from vehicles in
OL,4,Cfloods doubles since before pandemic `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe AA said these incidents are
OL,8,Fconsidered life-threatening as a car
OL,9,Fstuck in at least two feet of water
OL,10,Fcan float away to where it is
OL,11,Fimpossible for the occupants to
OL,12,Fescape, such as by getting stuck under
OL,13,Fbridges.
OL,15,FNine people had to be rescued from
OL,16,Fcars caught in floods in Greater
OL,17,FManchester and Powys, Wales, over one
OL,18,Fweekend last month.
