OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FPeak years for flood rescues from cars
OL,8,Foften match highs in the number of
OL,9,Ffloods.
OL,11,FTony Rich, the AA's road safety
OL,12,Fexpert, said flash flooding and sudden
OL,13,Fdownpours that overwhelm drainage are
OL,14,F"far more frequent than they used to
OL,15,Fbe".
OL,17,FBut he claimed cars getting stuck in
OL,18,Fwater is often "down to bad judgment
OL,19,Fby drivers".
