OL,3,CRescues of people from vehicles in
OL,4,Cfloods doubles since before pandemic `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHe said: "The ford or underpass that
OL,8,Fis usually driveable even with some
OL,9,Frain becomes a completely different
OL,10,Fobstacle after a deluge.
OL,12,F"You would hope that drivers might
OL,13,Fread the warning signs: severe
OL,14,Frainfall, kerbs that have disappeared
OL,15,Funderwater, obvious water flow or
OL,16,Findicated depth at fords.
OL,18,F"Unfortunately many don't, and a
OL,19,Fdrowned car is not a breakdown but an
OL,20,Finsurance job, likely a write-off."
