OL,3,CRescues of people from vehicles in
OL,4,Cfloods doubles since before pandemic `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FMr Rich suggested that signs warning
OL,8,Fof flooding hotspots could include
OL,9,Falternative routes, to "persuade more
OL,10,Fdrivers to turn round and not try
OL,11,Ftheir luck".
OL,13,FHe added: "In many cases, there isn't
OL,14,Fmuch that can be done to prevent
OL,15,Fdriver stupidity, but signage that
OL,16,Fdeters most examples of recklessness
OL,17,Fmay be more cost-effective than
OL,18,Fsending out roadworkers to close a
OL,19,Froad after an event or a fire engine
OL,20,Fto rescue vehicle occupants."
